    <p class="congrats">
        Congratulations! Looks like you already own rights to this game, you can download it right here!
    </p><br />
<div class="cxa-add-to-wishlist-component button">
			<a href="-/media/Blockchain/@token" class="btn">Download Now</a>
			</div><br />
    <p>Access powered by blockchain identity.</p>
</div>
